      "created_at": "2026-03-18T05:38:37.198Z",
      "response": "😴 **Ayurvedic Sleep Remedies:**\n\n• Bed by **10 PM** (Kapha time for deepest sleep)\n• Warm milk + pinch of nutmeg + cardamom at bedtime\n• Brahmi or Ashwagandha herb before sleep\n• Foot massage with warm sesame or brahmi oil\n• Avoid screens 1 hour before sleep\n• Yoga Nidra meditation (20 min) before bed\n• Keep bedroom cool, dark and quiet"
