      "created_at": "2026-03-19T06:10:47.327Z",
      "response": "🌿 **The Three Doshas:**\n\n1. **Vata** (Air + Space) — Movement, creativity, communication\n2. **Pitta** (Fire + Water) — Metabolism, digestion, intelligence\n3. **Kapha** (Earth + Water) — Structure, lubrication, stability\n\nEveryone has a unique mix called **Prakriti** (constitution). Imbalance (Vikriti) causes disease. Ayurveda restores balance through diet, lifestyle & herbs."
    },
